    volume: "33"
    pages: "11539-11551"
    url: "https://arxiv.org/abs/2006.16971"
    notes: "Proposes TTN: updating BN running statistics from test batches without gradient computation."

  - type: article
    title: "Test-Time Training with Self-Supervision for Generalization under Distribution Shifts"
    authors:
